                                &lt;/span&gt;
                                &lt;br clear="none"/&gt;Think about:&lt;br clear="none"/&gt;
                                &lt;ul&gt;
                                    &lt;li&gt;where you work, your job or college.&lt;/li&gt;
                                    &lt;li&gt;your strengths and skills.&lt;/li&gt;
                                    &lt;li&gt;your networks.&lt;/li&gt;
                                    &lt;li&gt;exercise.&lt;/li&gt;
                                &lt;/ul&gt;
                                &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;3. What do you like to do?&lt;/span&gt;
                                &lt;br clear="none"/&gt;
                                &lt;br clear="none"/&gt;Think about people you like to see, places you like to visit, activities you enjoy doing and your favourite tv programmes etc.&lt;br clear="none"/&gt;
                                &lt;br clear="none"/&gt;
                                &lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;4. What are your food preferences or requirements?&lt;/span&gt;
