                                                                &lt;br clear="none"/&gt;
                                                            &lt;/div&gt;
                                                        &lt;/div&gt;
                                                        &lt;div&gt;Where required codes are unavailable the free text field should be used and consideration given to the submission of a new code request to UK SNOMED CT request submission portal (see https://isd.digital.nhs.uk/rsp/user/guest/home.jsf). Contact info@thePRSB.org for further information. &lt;/div&gt;
