                                &lt;div&gt;Evening meal.│ Any bolus administered between 15.30 and 22.59. │ E.g., the ICR at evening meal.&lt;/div&gt;
                                &lt;div&gt;Other. │ Any bolus administered between 23.00 and 05.29 │ E.g., the ICR used for doses given at other times. This includes overnight.&lt;/div&gt;
