                                    &lt;br clear="none"/&gt;
                                &lt;/div&gt;
                                &lt;div&gt;New code request │ Manual suspend of insulin pump (procedure) │ No specific guidance.&lt;/div&gt;
                                &lt;div&gt;New code request │ Automated low glucose suspend of insulin pump (procedure) │ No specific guidance.&lt;/div&gt;
                                &lt;div&gt;New code request │ Automated predictive low glucose suspend of insulin pump (procedure) │ No specific guidance.&lt;/div&gt;
