                                &lt;div&gt;~By low glucose suspend system * (which "suspend insulin infusion when CGM glucose levels fall below a hypoglycaemia threshold...").&lt;/div&gt;
                                &lt;div&gt;~By predictive low glucose suspend (PLGS) system * (which "contain prediction algorithms that forecast future hypoglycaemia (e.g. within the next 20 min) and pre-emptively suspend insulin delivery before the occurrence of hypoglycaemia.").&lt;/div&gt;
                                &lt;div&gt;
