&lt;div&gt;Hybrid closed loop (HCL) systems are currently in use by people with diabetes and "are characterised by the coexistence of algorithm-driven automated insulin delivery combined with manual mealtime boluses [see https://doi.org/10.1111/dom.14273)]."&lt;br clear="none"/&gt;
