                                &lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
                                &lt;div&gt;[IU] │ international unit **│ Standard deviation.│ Units of standard deviation of a variable (i.e. Total daily dose (mean)) must match the units of the variable itself (i.e. international unit ).&lt;/div&gt;
                                &lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
                                &lt;div&gt;* UCUM codes are mixed case American Standard Code for Information Interchange (ASCII) text.&lt;/div&gt;
