                                &lt;div&gt;New code request │ Mean total hourly dose delivered by continuous intraperitoneal insulin infusion for time block (observable entity) │ No specific guidance. &lt;/div&gt;
                                &lt;div&gt;New code request │ Mean total daily insulin dose delivered by continuous intraperitoneal insulin infusion (observable entity) │ Use only if total time block duration is equal to 24 hours with a start time of 00:00 and an end time of 23:59. &lt;/div&gt;
